	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey,
<br />
<br />So I got the PGM burned to a 27c040 and it's wired up fine. The CHR is only 8k and I doubled it up to 32k and burned it to a 27c256 but I'm unsure of how to wire the 27c256 as the CHR on this MMC3 board. Any help would be great.
<br />
<br />Thanks!!

		

